            <div class="flex flex-col space-y text-black dark:text-white"><h3 class="font-semibold text-xl">
              Vision</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
                Our vision is a world where rice farming is not just a livelihood but a flourishing legacy passed down
                through generations. We envision a future where every farmer is equipped with the latest technologies,
                sustainable practices, and a strong support network. By bridging tradition and modernity, we aim to
                create a global community that values the art of rice cultivation, ensuring a bountiful harvest for
                today and a thriving legacy for tomorrow. Join us as we envision a world where the golden grains of rice
                sow the seeds of abundance and unity.
              </p></div>
